{"tid":410755,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"全台第一人？台果粉iP8用不到一天即爆Mon","createTime":"2017-09-23T08:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T09:14:37.000Z","uid":142633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e65a770b25c754ea179205fabd4addf0e0db244","tid":410755,"uid":142633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:15:54.000Z","msg":"全台第一人？台果粉iP8用不到一天即爆Mon<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果iPhone 8手機周五（22日）正式開賣，大陸網站便流傳一張iPhone 8 Plus機背玻璃穿了一個洞的照片，事件更被稱為iPhone 8全球首碎的個案。而在周六（23日）的凌晨，台灣也傳出可能是iPhone 8全球首個「爆Mon」的個案。 <br />\n<br />\n雖然蘋果iPhone 8周五開賣被指為歷來iPhone開售最慘淡的一次，但仍有不少果粉第一時間便入手了新手機。在網上討論批踢踢實業坊便有網民表示自己周五一早衝去手機專門店買了一部iPhone 8，晚上帶着手機前往健身，誰知放在運動褲的手機一下子跌了出來，手機屏幕隨即粉碎。發文者又附上手機「出事」後的照片，可見屏幕滿佈裂痕令人慘不忍睹，至於機背則完好無缺。發文者於是問大家可以將手機拿到哪裏維修。 <br />\n<br />\n不少人看後開玩笑稱「你應該第一個送修的」、「賀！全台第一人」、「最速傳說」；有人更指「加修理費夠買iPhone X了」；又因為有人指維修屏幕所費不菲，更建議「直接買一隻新的比較快」。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/news/20170923/bkntw-20170923093458724-0923_04011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170923%2Fbkntw-20170923093458724-0923_04011_001.html&d=4cPfoMSL9U39dwI9uzNim%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=429db096\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/news/20170923/bkntw-20170923093458724-0923_04011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">眼紅者勿入</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6e82802f5ed0f5a8d5ecef6cdc7617722ff46c","tid":410755,"uid":142633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bb12cc39fdbee006246d5f4efdb4cce1bbec2f","tid":410755,"uid":142633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"【一跌即碎】iP8入手唔夠半日爛成咁 兩岸苦主網上呻慘<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170923&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57245816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170923%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57245816&d=4cPfoMSL9U39dwI9uzNim%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=d20632ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170923%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57245816&h=05a1362e\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170923&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57245816</a>"},{"pid":"e530793cbed7a077fb05b10ba300f8303771447c","tid":410755,"uid":142633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f32142d56509308ac7e9765bde67a59cd04e2e","tid":410755,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"搏上位"},{"pid":"0e13d251842e0db9835ffd28e9cbd293284292b0","tid":410755,"uid":142633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb75b04ad36c350f355c5646d96ce3c6234c39af","tid":410755,"uid":89220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:14:37.000Z","msg":"呃鬼咩爛到咁同我講喺gym房整跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跌落地再唔小心俾啞鈴壓中？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}